## Interface Adapters

Interface Adapters convert data between use cases/entities and external agencies.

### Controllers (Driving Adapters)

```java
// Converts HTTP request to use case input
@RestController
@RequiredArgsConstructor
class OrderController {
  private final PlaceOrderUseCase placeOrderUseCase;
  
  @PostMapping("/orders")
  public ResponseEntity<PlaceOrderResponse> placeOrder(@RequestBody @Valid PlaceOrderRequest request) {
    PlaceOrderInput input = toInput(request);
    PlaceOrderOutput output = placeOrderUseCase.execute(input);
    return ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.CREATED).body(toResponse(output));
  }
  
  private PlaceOrderInput toInput(PlaceOrderRequest request) {
    return new PlaceOrderInput(
      request.lines().stream()
        .map(l -> new OrderLineInput(l.productId(), l.quantity()))
        .toList(),
      new ShippingAddressInput(
        request.shipping().street(),
        request.shipping().city(),
        request.shipping().zip()
      )
    );
  }
}
```

### Gateways (Driven Adapters)

```java
// Interface (defined in use case circle)
public interface OrderGateway {
  Optional<Order> findById(OrderId id);
  void save(Order order);
}

// Implementation (in interfaceadapter/gateway/)
@Repository
@RequiredArgsConstructor
class JpaOrderGateway implements OrderGateway {
  private final SpringDataOrderRepository repository;
  
  @Override
  public Optional<Order> findById(OrderId id) {
    return repository.findById(id.value()).map(this::toDomain);
  }
  
  @Override
  public void save(Order order) {
    repository.save(toEntity(order));
  }
  
  private Order toDomain(OrderEntity entity) {
    return Order.reconstitute(/* ... */);
  }
  
  private OrderEntity toEntity(Order order) {
    return OrderEntity.builder()
      .id(order.getId().value())
      .status(order.getStatus())
      .build();
  }
}
```

